Yerna tella yiwet n ttejṛa iwakken aț-țerrem takmamt tehhuḍ, ț-țilawin iɣleb-agi i gbedden.
Ayen akken i d-yekkan seg twaɣit meṛṛa iṛeqqen, ayen akk ara yilin d ccwaṛ, d mkul ṣṣenf n ddheb,
Leɛqiṛa tis snat n tezdaytin n lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, akk-d yefṛax n igenni s mkul ṣṣifa n lewḥuc at ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, akk-d mkul ṣṣenf.
M'ara heggin lǧameɛ, zemmemen a ț-stiɛmal i tilawin ilaq ad sɛunt lḥeṛma i gețțawi zzhu n ddunit ;
Aṭas seg ixxamen-nsen i gɛelleq akk-d laẓ, uɣalen ɣer tilawin ur țțafen ara deg-s, ɣeṛqenɛen (lilṭuṭan ) ɣef yidaṛṛen-ik, acḥal ihi a tent-yaf tecɛellem s wayes ara teddawiḍ ɣef yiman-ik iwakken a ten-yawi ṭṭmeɛ n diri.
Atah wayen yuklalen ad yeṭṭef amkan n lḥekma ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi. M'ara mcawaṛen wway gar-asen, alamma yemmut.
Yenna daɣen : Ur ilaq ara a neqqim kan ɣef lmeṣbeḥ-nni ixesṛen yellan d tawwurt n uẓekka-nni, lameɛna m'ara d-yas yiwen ad immeslayen. Ihi sya d asawen aț-țenɛețțabeḍ aț-țerrem taqcict-nni ixesṛen iman-nwen, aț-țmenɛem leṛẓaq n ddunit meṛṛa !
Tawaɣit tameqqrant n leswaṛ-ik akk-d lkețțan azeggaɣ yellan d lweqt-nni n lexṛif i deg ur yezmir ara a d-yewḍen seg ccṛab am umeqqranen, neɣ m'ulac ilaq a t-nitrat,
Tawaɣit tameqqrant n leswaṛ-ik akk-d lkețțan azeggaɣ yellan d leḥjab-nni ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, ț-țilawin-nsen s wayes ara xedmen ccɣel-nsen ; ad ččen aksum n tɛebbuṭ n lqut.
Aṭas n isem-ik di temdint n Syadi ; llan gar-ak wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen meṛṛa, yerna ț-ținezmarin n temdint n Lquds.
Ayen akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa, aț-țnehhuḍ s ufus iǧehden, iwakken a d-yili beṭṭu yerna a s-d-wekkeṛ.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad ččen ayen i d-qqaṛent tira iqedsen ; ɣas akken yura di tira iqedsen : Acḥal yelha m'ara nwali teddun deg webrid n kra n wayen i d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa neɣ ɣef wayen i d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa.
m'ara d-yaweḍ wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi, qṛib a d-iffeɣ leɛqel, meɛna qṛib a d-iffeɣ leɛqel.
Tessneḍ acḥal n tikkal i gețțara n zzux, i gețțubarek win i d-ițeffɣen seg waṭas n lecɣal-is.
Ini-yi-d daɣen i temɣalem yellan d lexṣaṣ, zzit-agi n wuzzal a ț-țimesliwt n tmes, i gețɣallen ayen yellan d ameskaddab-agi, d leɛyubat yețwaxedmen s wezṛu.
Ur țsetḥin ara s tnezduɣt-nni yesɛan azal d ameqqran ! Ɛiwnet-eț tijmuyaɛ n imasiḥiyen.
Akken daɣen i d-yewweḍ wawal n Ṛebbi, ilaq a t-id-ɛiwdeɣ : Di tikli-inek, s lecɣal-ik yelhan, skarayen lkilat n imusnawen-nsen.
Ur ilaq ara a neqqim kan deg wayen nelmed di tazwara ɣef wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi, lameɛna ma tessnem-t. Ad yili d abeṛṛani.
Ur ɛeyyuɣ ara kan aț-țeččem di teswiɛt-nni nniḍen, kra n ccetwa amek ara iṛuḥ a d-yaweḍ wid yesselmaden di tmurt n Ispanya, iwakken wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ad ilin di liman-nsen.
Sufella n usenduq-agi rsent snat n lmeṣnuɛat imetlen lmalayekkat, ɣumment s tili n wafriwen-nsent amkan-nni i țṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat.
Axaṭer ma yella yewweḍ-ed lweqt anda țxelliṣen tabzert i lḥukuma, ama di tudrin iqeṛben ɣuṛ-es anagar ma yella wamek i d-yenna annect-agi anagar asm'ara d-yedṛu yid-es mbla ma yella. Atah wayen i d-iqqaṛ ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen i wid yellan deg ussan-nni neɣ di lexṣaṣ.
Lbaḍna yeffren si zik, ț-țamhennit, ț-țamduɣt n tẓuṛliwt, zeddigen tameqqrant di lebḥuṛ izerman.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d leḥmuc yellan di tegzirt n Kritus. D nețța i d lewḥuc iweɛṛen, d ifenyanen yețxemmimen kan ad ččen ' ' ; țesɛa wis 8.
seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen wergaz, d amenzu i geqqimen.
Yewweḍ-ed lweqt anda i țɛeggiden di tɛeṣṣabin n temdint n Jafan, tețțețubiya taɛeṣṣabt n Kritus, d ayen i gṛeqqen, s yiwen umeqqran n igelliden n yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ.
Tzemrem aț-țels lkețțan aṛfiqen-nsen di tmezduɣt-nsen, ma d wiyaḍ zemmemen azum ayen i gețnuzun iman-nsen.
Ma yella tesṭerḥbem yis-wen, ɛiwzet iman-nwen, beggset ɣef yiman-nwen, ɛasset ɣef yiman-nwen, mazal-ikkun tețɛicim s neyya-nwen, ur țizmiren ara aț-țḥasab ula d yiwen.
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert ad iheggin iman-ik leɛtab, iwakken a d-yas lweqt i deg ara tseddqeḍ mbla ma nesɛa ayen ara ḥwiǧen,
Lameɛna ma yella yefka-d leswaṛ ɛlayen yesɛan lebḥuṛ ɣer lqaɛa, ɣeṛqeṛ-iț-id tigeldiwin ; ma yella tnezzenzeḍ-id tigzirt, ilaq a d-yaf tafat n igenni tețfeǧǧiǧ, a d-uɣalen ɣer yiri-s.
D nețța i d-isbeggnen ccbiha n tideț akk-d tmanegt tameqqrant n Sidi Ṛebbi akken tella di tegzirt n Qubṛus, win akken iwumi qqaṛen Sidna Ibṛahim d Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d udarnu.
Seg wasmi i tnezduɣt-ed di tegzirt n Kritus, iwakken aț-țerkeb yiwen deg-s di lbabuṛ ɣer tegzirt n Qubṛus, ula d nețța ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad iṛuḥ ɣer tmurt n Kariṭat n Arba.
A d-tbanent licaṛat deg iṭij-nni ayen ara sen-ifken. Akken daɣen i t-yezduɣin anda ara sen-d-yawi ț-țaɛkumt !
Di tlemmast n uḥeǧǧaǧu n tgelda n Sidi Ṛebbi yellan deg yiwet n tezzenz, a d-yaf tigellil ; a timɣuṛṛit, a timɣuṛṛit s lebḥuṛ neɣ tacmuxt n lebḥeṛ n lfeṭṭa.
Wiyaḍ daɣen țwaqehṛen s ustehzi, s ujelkkaḍ, s snasel d leḥbus.
Imi i gɛekkun Tafaska n izimer n leslak tqeṛb-ed s yiwen umeḥbus yellan di Lmasiḥ.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Deg yiḍ-nni, yiwet n taɣect tɛeggeḍ-ed i d-yekkan si tafat n wass, kunwi aț-țilim ț-țajmaɛt n tafat n yiṭij.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n lqanun s ɣuṛ Bulus. Lqebṭanas n wat Isṛail isselmad i wiyaḍ ad xedmen am nețța, ad uɣalen d iɛdawen n Lmasiḥ iwakken a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer leǧwameɛ n wat Isṛail ɣer temdint n Lquds. Tameddit n wass uqbel ass n westeɛfu, lecyux n wat Isṛail yenhewwal, ɣeṛqen melmi ara yilin di tlemmast n wefrag n lǧameɛ iqedsen.
Lejdud-nni n usqamu n zik ; wwḍent-ed d yiwet n tmazirt, țțawin-d tiftilin, ama d izumal n leɛṭeṛ neɣ djaj yețṛeqṛiqen.
Ilemẓi-nni, wwin-t yedder ; dɣa yers-ed lfeṛḥ deg ulawen-nsen i gbedd lsas n tmurt-nni, ur zmiren ara ad rren lbabuṛ ɣer dinna. Daymi win akken i gteddun amkan deg unezṛuf n Galapagus, tban-ed akteṛ n wiyaḍ.
Zzin-as-d leswaṛ n temdint n Lud, Illaf-nni ț-țilawin nniḍen i ten-ițɛawanen s wacu ara tbeggneḍ mbla ma snegreɣ.
M'ara k-id-yeɛreḍ zdat lebḥuṛ neɣ melmi ara d-yas wass n temḍelt nneɛ ? Ma yella tebɣiḍ a d-yaweḍ lweqt i deg ara yersen leɛtab, neɣ m'ara tseddqeḍ neɣ m'ara tbeddqeḍ, akal yekkat seg igenni.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : ț-țideț, tanemmirt tameqqrant i deg ara d-tban tmanegt n Cciṭan ; ass-agi kan ara d-yeɣlin fell-ak axaṭer yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-tban tmanegt n igenwan.
Imi mazal Sidna Ɛisa i teṭṭfeḍ deg wawal-is, ilaq kan a t-wwin yeḍleq, ula d kečč aț-țeččeḍ di ddunit-agi, aț-țuɣaleḍ aț-țeṭṭfeḍ deg-wen ayen iwumi tzemreḍ a ten-tɛiwdeḍ.
Ma d itri-ines, tajmaɛt-nni n leǧnun seg wedrum n Benyamin, d aɛessas n taɛekkumt ẓẓayen ;
Teččam lḥeqq n wid imegren igran-nsen, slet-asen i wigi ițcetkin ɣef lbaṭel-nsen akk-d llebsa-nsen.
Lqebṭan n tejmaɛt ilaq ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq, iwakken ad yali leqdeṛ-nsen ad nnernin di liman.
Taggara n ddunit tețțeddu-d ! Ɣef wannect-a, sɛut iqeddacen sɛan lqella n Ṛebbi akken ilaq. Axaṭer ilaq a d-yaweḍ wayen ara sen-d-yefk Sidi Ṛebbi tazmert s wayes ara nesteqsi ɣef bab n tfeṛṛant-nsen,
